  "content": "<p data-pid=\"gfW-Jwl2\">Notion 的功能可太多了。。。完全覆盖 Notion 功能的笔记软件估计没有。</p><p data-pid=\"WlW3HP4A\">但是结合 Anki 间隔重复功能的笔记软件还是有的，比如 RemNote、Logseq 等等。</p><p data-pid=\"Ueps4prR\">由于我只用过 RemNote，所以就简单介绍一下：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2eaac8a666b92cce952aa3422f4de97_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1428\" data-rawheight=\"1176\" data-original-token=\"v2-c2eaac8a666b92cce952aa3422f4de97\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a4af503f71799e53407ea2c3b18a904_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1428\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c2eaac8a666b92cce952aa3422f4de97_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1428&#39; height=&#39;1176&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1428\" data-rawheight=\"1176\" data-original-token=\"v2-c2eaac8a666b92cce952aa3422f4de97\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7a4af503f71799e53407ea2c3b18a904_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1428\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-c2eaac8a666b92cce952aa3422f4de97_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2eaac8a666b92cce952aa3422f4de97_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"-jXmBoHV\">如图所示，RemNote 是一款大纲笔记。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3abfddc799d866154dee2b5ede306560_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2008\" data-rawheight=\"1236\" data-original-token=\"v2-3abfddc799d866154dee2b5ede306560\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9666e98612f0f817423371143dfc4447_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2008\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-3abfddc799d866154dee2b5ede306560_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;2008&#39; height=&#39;1236&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2008\" data-rawheight=\"1236\" data-original-token=\"v2-3abfddc799d866154dee2b5ede306560\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-9666e98612f0f817423371143dfc4447_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2008\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-3abfddc799d866154dee2b5ede306560_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3abfddc799d866154dee2b5ede306560_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"VbsqzX5A\">其内置了各种制卡语法，可以让你在写笔记的同时制作抽认卡，然后间隔重复。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d20348aa93c6c5cba9afb9399ce3f145_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2180\" data-rawheight=\"1166\" data-original-token=\"v2-d20348aa93c6c5cba9afb9399ce3f145\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcb28a5d7970bc491980552708848130_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2180\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d20348aa93c6c5cba9afb9399ce3f145_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;2180&#39; height=&#39;1166&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2180\" data-rawheight=\"1166\" data-original-token=\"v2-d20348aa93c6c5cba9afb9399ce3f145\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-dcb28a5d7970bc491980552708848130_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2180\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d20348aa93c6c5cba9afb9399ce3f145_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d20348aa93c6c5cba9afb9399ce3f145_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"D3_ZVN3O\">另外 RemNote 支持双向链接，这一点在数学上特别有用：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a3e451dd38933795ca94c0eb72d9cea3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2412\" data-rawheight=\"1394\" data-original-token=\"v2-a3e451dd38933795ca94c0eb72d9cea3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f58d99ff883e24bc13920c16180e78ea_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2412\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a3e451dd38933795ca94c0eb72d9cea3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;2412&#39; height=&#39;1394&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2412\" data-rawheight=\"1394\" data-original-token=\"v2-a3e451dd38933795ca94c0eb72d9cea3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f58d99ff883e24bc13920c16180e78ea_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2412\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a3e451dd38933795ca94c0eb72d9cea3_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a3e451dd38933795ca94c0eb72d9cea3_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"moP5cWrq\">更多有关 RemNote 的内容，我推荐阅读：</p><p data-pid=\"SWZJDhYL\"><a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/6fd40f6ff16c5f4f3f46871d3d9ea801\" data-hash=\"6fd40f6ff16c5f4f3f46871d3d9ea801\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$6fd40f6ff16c5f4f3f46871d3d9ea801\">@何问宇</a> 的 RemNote 教程：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/350209298\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0fb9403be0e09cc63ddd0c6dad9f5bff_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"999\" data-image-height=\"411\" class=\"internal\">何问宇：结构化突击学习的利器--RemNote, 吹爆!</a><p data-pid=\"Vae4StXz\">我的简单官方教程翻译：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/235834139\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-69332e1ed99be3e7652a24950ca087e5_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1454\" data-image-height=\"849\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：5 分钟了解 Remnote</a><p></p>",
